---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Project Dossier">
  <!-- Hero Section -->
  <section class="blueprint-grid-hero">
    <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 py-12 sm:py-16">
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-5 gap-10 lg:gap-12 items-center">
        <!-- Left: Text (3 columns) -->
        <div class="lg:col-span-3">
          <span class="badge mb-4 inline-block">Closed Beta</span>
          <h1 class="text-stone-900 mb-4">Open Working Hours</h1>
          <p class="text-xl text-stone-600 mb-4">
            Privacy-preserving infrastructure for documenting and aggregating healthcare working conditions.
          </p>
          <a href="/dashboard" class="inline-flex items-center gap-1.5 text-teal-600 hover:text-teal-700 font-medium text-sm">
            See current coverage across Germany →
          </a>
        </div>

        <!-- Right: Phone Mockup (2 columns) -->
        <div class="lg:col-span-2 flex justify-center lg:justify-end">
          <div class="phone-mockup-small">
            <div class="phone-screen">
              <img
                src="/screenshots/status-dashboard.png"
                alt="Status Dashboard showing 14-day work hours overview"
              />
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Problem Statement -->
  <section class="section-alt py-12 sm:py-16">
    <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6">
      <div class="max-w-3xl">
        <h2 class="text-stone-900 mb-4">Problem</h2>
        <div class="prose text-stone-700 space-y-4">
          <p>
            <strong>Chronic overwork in healthcare</strong> carries real human cost: exhaustion, long-term health damage, professional burnout. Patients face increased risk through higher error rates and compromised care quality.
          </p>
          <p>
            These costs are <strong>largely externalized</strong>:
          </p>
          <ul class="space-y-2 ml-4">
            <li><strong>Not reflected</strong> in staffing decisions or planning.</li>
            <li><strong>Only partially</strong> captured in incident reports.</li>
            <li><strong>Rarely appear</strong> as systemic evidence in legal or bargaining contexts.</li>
          </ul>
          <p>
            Unsafe working conditions can persist – even where formal protections exist.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Analytical Perspective -->
  <section class="py-12 sm:py-16">
    <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6">
      <div class="max-w-3xl">
        <h2 class="text-stone-900 mb-4">Analysis</h2>
        <div class="prose text-stone-700 space-y-4">
          <p>
            The problem is <strong>not missing rules, but missing information</strong>.
          </p>
          <p>
            Working time regulations exist. Enforcement mechanisms exist. But <strong>systemic evidence of actual working patterns</strong> – aggregated, verifiable, independent of employer reporting – is largely absent.
          </p>
          <p>
            Without this evidence:
          </p>
          <ul class="space-y-2 ml-4">
            <li><strong>Complaints remain anecdotal</strong> and easy to dismiss.</li>
            <li><strong>Unions lack data</strong> for collective bargaining.</li>
            <li><strong>Regulators can't identify</strong> systemic patterns.</li>
          </ul>
          <p>
            <strong>The problem is infrastructural.</strong>
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Solution -->
  <section class="section-alt py-12 sm:py-16">
    <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6">
      <div class="max-w-3xl">
        <h2 class="text-stone-900 mb-4">Solution</h2>
        <div class="prose text-stone-700 space-y-4">
          <p>
            <strong>Open Working Hours</strong> provides this infrastructure: a mobile app for documenting actual working hours, with privacy-preserving aggregation that produces systemic evidence.
          </p>
        </div>

        <!-- Solution Details -->
        <ul class="mt-6 space-y-4 text-stone-700">
          <li class="flex gap-3">
            <span class="text-teal-600 font-semibold select-none">1.</span>
            <span><strong>What it is:</strong> An iOS app for tracking actual working hours – automatically via geofencing or manually in seconds.</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex gap-3">
            <span class="text-teal-600 font-semibold select-none">2.</span>
            <span><strong>For whom:</strong> Physicians, nurses, and healthcare professionals who want to contribute to transparency.</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex gap-3">
            <span class="text-teal-600 font-semibold select-none">3.</span>
            <span><strong>Output:</strong> Aggregated, anonymized statistics – by region, specialty, role level.</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex gap-3">
            <span class="text-teal-600 font-semibold select-none">4.</span>
            <span><strong>Status:</strong> iOS app in closed beta. Backend deployed. Seeking pilot partners.</span>
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Principles -->
  <section class="py-12 sm:py-16">
    <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6">
      <div class="max-w-3xl">
        <h2 class="text-stone-900 mb-4">Principles</h2>
        <ul class="space-y-3 text-stone-700">
          <li class="flex gap-3">
            <span class="text-teal-600 mt-1">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m6 2a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z" />
              </svg>
            </span>
            <span><strong>Low friction:</strong> Automatic tracking via geofencing. Manual entry in seconds.</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex gap-3">
            <span class="text-teal-600 mt-1">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m6 2a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z" />
              </svg>
            </span>
            <span><strong>Not an employer tool:</strong> Data belongs to users. No third-party access.</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex gap-3">
            <span class="text-teal-600 mt-1">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m6 2a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z" />
              </svg>
            </span>
            <span><strong>Privacy by design:</strong> Individual data never published. Only aggregated statistics with k-anonymity.</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex gap-3">
            <span class="text-teal-600 mt-1">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m6 2a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z" />
              </svg>
            </span>
            <span><strong>Full control:</strong> Data export and deletion anytime. GDPR compliant.</span>
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Evidence Links -->
  <section class="border-t border-stone-200 py-8">
    <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6">
      <h3 class="text-stone-500 text-sm font-medium uppercase tracking-wide mb-4">Learn more</h3>
      <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-x-8 gap-y-2 text-stone-700">
        <a href="/product" class="hover:text-teal-600">View product demo</a>
        <a href="/privacy" class="hover:text-teal-600">Read privacy principles</a>
        <a href="/team" class="hover:text-teal-600">Team & Contact</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
